ypes\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\"}, {\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9971335911733917, \"rank\": 0.0013434838231923246, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9999181647419125, \"rank\": 7.930078479924153e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During qualifying, four members of each five-woman team will compete on each event, with teams dropping their lowest score.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top eight teams will advance to the team final on Tuesday.Here's how to watch Biles in action.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch NBC 4 free wherever you are  Biles will serve as the anchor, or final competitor on balance beam, floor exercise and vault.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will go next-to-last for the U.S. on uneven bars,where she has submitted an original skillto the International Gymnastics Federation.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Gymnastics Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Biles successfully completes the maneuver during qualifying, it will be entered into the sport's Code of Points, where it will carry her name.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old superstar already has five elements named for her in the code.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the top 24 individual qualifiers in the all-around will move on to the all-around finals scheduled for Aug. 1, with the caveat that no team may have more than two gymnasts.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Americans are looking to return to the top of the podium after finishing second to Russia in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.2921502821877833e-13, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.8580405245681761, \"rank\": 0.12604759584453276, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8137545297663931, \"rank\": 0.22867375701388373, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"July 28 - Team Qualifying: Simone Biles will first compete on Sunday, July 28 in team qualifying events begin at 3:30 a.m.\", \"from\": 1